"Why, we're drinking pretend tea, of course! It's ever so delicious!" He raises his cup to his lips and takes an exaggerated sip. "Delightful!"

"Pretend tea? Bah, that's fancy talk!" you say. "Gimmie a good ol' tin can fulla garbage juice any day!"

"My word!" says Darling Jeremiah, recoiling in horror. "How scandalous!"
> take teapot

> take teapot
