"My word!" says Darling Jeremiah, "Theft! Misappropriation! Scandal! Oh, constable, do help!"

"You shut yer yap," you say, "I'm a rough, tough urchin an' I'll bust any constable in the noodle wot tries ta stop me! You'd best quit the chin music if'n ya know what's good for ya."

Your threat has the desired effect. Jeremiah shuts his mouth, though he continues to glare at you crossly.
