> look through telescopes
"Ooo, I wonder what all them crumbums is up to now!" you say, squinting through a conveniently close telescope. "Really, Rags? Don't you have more pressing matters to attend to than spying?"  You shuffle your feet. "Crumbs, Percy, I'm jest gonna take a quick gander!"

You squint through one of the random telescopes:
You see Good Little Eustace sleeping soundly in his bed, visions of sugar plums (presumably) dancing in his head. No Santa yet, though.
