> hypnotize doctor

> hypnotize doctor
"Oy, doc! Take a look at me new pocketwatch!"

"Hmm?" Dr. Caligazzi turns to look as you dangle the watch back and forth.  Instinctively, her eyes follow the arc of the swinging watch, back and forth, back and forth.

"Yer gettin' sleepy, doc!" you say, "Now you is under me control! You is gonna do whatever I tells ya ta do now!"

"You is getting really sleepy now!" You feels like you can't control yer eyes."

"Like, ya just gotta sleep. Ya can't keep yer eyes open."

"Ya just wanna do whatever Lil' Ragamuffin tells ya to do!"

"You is totally under Lil' Ragamuffin's control now! Ya can't resist doin' whatever she tells ya to do! And she is me, so ya better listen to me too!"

Dr. Caligazzi's eyes gradually go blank and she slumps down in her chair. "Yes... yes that sounds right...," she mumbles.

Holy schlamoly! You can't believe that actually worked!
