"Oy Percy, how kin we fix this elevator?"

"Lucky for us, Rags, I also studied electrical engineering while I was a student at Oxford. First you'll need the right tool: A 3 inch double flange-gripper with a self-puncturing hectometer."

"Wot? I ain't never heard o' such a thing. Wot's that do?"

"Well,,,you would push it into that hole and twist it around until it got the wires to connect--"

"That don't sound so hard. Couldn't I jest use, like, a stick or somethin'?"

